dmca.title: Cease and Desist Trademark/Service Infringement
dmca.body:
The document has not been OCR'd, but exists in jpg form at the following URL. We have handled the matter to our satisfaction, and require no assistance; however, we wish to submit the incident to be included in your database as a public service.
